    gets heavy fast from the opertations and marching loop calls.

    I originaly tried to figuring out the surface to cube map thing, thinking
    drawing would be easier, but quickly I failed from lack of math skills. 

    However Shane's comment had the basic formula I had wrong. With
    some research and understanding of his very cool 'Dice' shader I was able
    to rework my original code to use this method. I feel that I have almost 
