    // Reflection loop based off @BigWings tutorial.
    // https://youtu.be/beNDx5Cvt7M

    // Bits and pieces - most folks here prob know this stuff.    
    // http://web.cs.wpi.edu/~emmanuel/courses/cs4731/A14/slides/lecture21.pdf

    // @Shane's very cool moving dice shader
    // https://www.shadertoy.com/view/3sVBDd


